## Description {#details}

A single machine location; its Kind is either a register, spill location, or immediate value.

If the VarLoc is not a NonEntryValueKind, then it will use only a single <a href="/docs/api/structs/anonymous-namespace-varlocbasedimpl-cpp-/varlocbasedldv/varloc/machineloc">MachineLoc</a> of RegisterKind.
